flowchart TD
 A[Alert or User Report] --> B{Business impact?}
 B -->|Critical| C[Declare P1 Incident]
 B -->|High| D[Assign P2 Engineer]
 B -->|Standard| E[Service Desk Queue]
 C --> F[Incident Channel and Stakeholder Update]
 D --> G[Technical Investigation]
 E --> G
 F --> G
 G --> H{Service restored?}
 H -->|No| I[Escalate to Specialist or Vendor]
 I --> G
 H -->|Yes| J[Validate with Users and Monitoring]
 J --> K[Close Incident]
 K --> L[Root-Cause Analysis and Actions]
